name: Butternut Squash Fries
description: A deliciously savoury alternative to potato fries!

ingredients.name: butternut squash
ingredients.additionalInstruction: peeled, seeded and cut into 16 — 3/4” strips

preparation: Lightly spray Sheet Pan with vegetable oil.
Place squash sticks on Sheet Pan. Season with sriracha seasoning, toss in oil to coat and arrange in single layer. Season with Chili Garlic Sea Salt.
Roast, turning once, for approximately 14–18 minutes, or until golden.

products.name: Sheet Pan
summary: Lightweight all-purpose baking sheet made from a single piece of aluminum, with a one-inch rim.
